From the Infowars web site :: On this Wednesday, August 14 broadcast of The Alex Jones Show, Alex interviews award-winning television reporter and investigative journalist Ben Swann. Alex speaks with Swann about his launch of the crowd source funded "Truth in Media Project" that allowed him to continue production of his show Full Disclosure which he began after leaving Cincinnati's Fox19 in late May. 

Alex interviews health expert Dr. Joseph Mercola about Coca-Cola's latest Ad defending the cancer causing artificial sweetener aspartame. 

Alex will also delve into how the federal government ran a $98 billion deficit last month, but the nation's debt remains unchanged for the 87th straight day. 

Alex will also discuss the continued eruption of violence throughout Egypt that left 95 dead and more than 200 wounded overnight. 

Alex continues to unveil the horrors of Obamacare which has now awarded Planned Parenthood $375,000 to help enroll participants in Obamacare.
